        <h3 class="faq-question-text" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">How Do I Activate My Product?</h3>
        <span class="accordion-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-accordion-content accordion-content">
        <div class="faq-answer-text" style="margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-gray);">
          1. Open the Zaat App.<br>
          2. Navigate to Product Activation.<br>
          3. Tap Activate Product.<br>
          4. Hold your phone near the NFC product.<br>
          5. Follow the on-screen instructions.<br><br>
          Once activation is complete, the product will automatically connect to your profile.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

